### Login to get token
POST http://localhost:3003/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Add a new blog with authentication (replace TOKEN with actual token from login)
POST http://localhost:3003/api/blogs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "title": "Authenticated Blog",
  "author": "Authenticated Author",
  "url": "https://authenticated.com",
  "likes": 15
}

### Delete a blog with authentication (replace BLOG_ID and TOKEN with actual values)
DELETE http://localhost:3003/api/blogs/BLOG_ID
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
